stablish named endowed funds begin at $100000 and receive annual financial reports from the university the haas center carefully stewards each gift providing customized information about the public service activities your support makes possible personalized stewardship plans typically include narrative reports on program activities letters from students and staff recognition in the haas center triennial report and invitation to haas center events leadership donors are encouraged to meet with staff and students whenever possible and we work closely with donors to develop other avenues for engagement based on interest and opportunity for more information please contact suzanne abel educating for equity community programs toward a better world public service leadership from scholarship to solutions pacs center beyond our borders international public service general support buy a brick up educating for equity community programs groups haas center for public service printer friendly version connect with us facebook facebook twitter twitter video icon video stanford seal newsletter giving to haas action logo support our work haas center for public service 562 salvatierra walk stanford ca 94305 650 723 0992 hours m f 8 5 support our work feedback copyright 2011 stanford university terms of use copyright complaints report a problem with this site
